                    <bibl xml:id="bib1144-6">ms Damas, Patriarcat syrien orthodoxe, cod. 12/17 (olim ms Dayr az-Za‘faran, cod. parch. 18 (Dolabany)), f. 127v-128</bibl>
                </note>
